## AI Workflow

This project uses a 3-agent workflow (Planner, Implementer, Reviewer) with file-based coordination.

### Start a new development cycle

```bash
scripts/ai-start-cycle.sh feature/<scope>
```

### Run agents

```bash
scripts/ai-plan.sh          # Start planner (default: claude)
scripts/ai-implement.sh     # Start implementer (default: codex)
scripts/ai-review.sh        # Start reviewer (default: claude)
```

### Create a PR

```bash
scripts/ai-pr.sh sync
```

See `CLAUDE.md` for full workflow rules.
